ises-showed-no-interest-peace-2024-05-27/</link><description>一位访问台北的美国高级议员周一表示，台湾订购的武器终于在路上，中国上周的“恐吓”军事演习凸显了增强台湾威慑能力的必要性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 04:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-lawmaker-says-chinas-intimidating-military-exercises-showed-no-interest-peace-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中共高级官员在瓦努阿图举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/senior-chinese-communist-party-official-vanuatu-meetings-2024-05-27/</link><description>中国共产党高级官员刘建超周一在访问这个受到北京和美国欢迎的太平洋岛国时会见了瓦努阿图总理夏洛特·萨尔瓦伊。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 04:10:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/senior-chinese-communist-party-official-vanuatu-meetings-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>清算人完成股权出售交易后，中国恒大电动汽车部门股价飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shares-china-evergrandes-ev-unit-soar-after-liquidators-stake-sale-deal-2024-05-27/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车集团表示，清算人已代表主要股东同意出售这家电动汽车制造商的股份，该公司周一恢复交易，该公司股价周一上涨了一倍多。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shares-china-evergrandes-ev-unit-soar-after-liquidators-stake-sale-deal-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国四川省发生5.0级地震</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/earthquake-magnitude-50-hits-chinas-sichuan-province-2024-05-27/</link><description>据中国地震台网中心周一消息，中国四川省木里县发生5.0级地震。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/earthquake-magnitude-50-hits-chinas-sichuan-province-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>在中国，星巴克试图避免价格战却陷入打折潮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-starbucks-tries-avoid-price-war-gets-dragged-into-discounting-2024-05-27/</link><description>随着星巴克在中国的啤酒业务面临着来自快速增长、低成本竞争对手的激烈竞争，这些竞争对手已经蚕食了星巴克的市场份额，这家咖啡连锁店正越来越多地被拖入其声称希望避免的价格战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:33:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-starbucks-tries-avoid-price-war-gets-dragged-into-discounting-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-05-27/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国设立第三只基金 475 亿美元提振半导体行业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-sets-up-475-bln-state-fund-boost-semiconductor-industry-2024-05-27/</link><description>根据向政府运营的公司注册处提交的文件，中国已计划设立第三个国家支持投资基金，以促进半导体行业发展，注册资本为 3440 亿元人民币（475 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:11:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-sets-up-475-bln-state-fund-boost-semiconductor-industry-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国“资产荒”抑制央行债券交易雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/asset-famine-china-curbs-central-banks-bond-trading-ambitions-2024-05-27/</link><description>中国金融部门低风险资产的稀缺正在阻碍央行在中断17年后重返国债市场以提高其货币政策工具箱效率的计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:55:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/asset-famine-china-curbs-central-banks-bond-trading-ambitions-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>发言人称日本要求朝鲜取消卫星火箭发射</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-demands-north-korea-cancel-satellite-rocket-launch-spokesperson-says-2024-05-27/</link><description>日本政府最高发言人、内阁官房长官林芳正周一表示，东京已通过北京的外交渠道要求朝鲜取消计划的卫星火箭发射。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-demands-north-korea-cancel-satellite-rocket-launch-spokesperson-says-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产开发商佳兆业清算听证会延期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-court-adjourns-liquidation-hearing-china-developer-kaisa-2024-05-27/</link><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求佳兆业集团清算的请愿书的听证会推迟至 6 月 24 日，这让这家陷入困境的中国开发商在实施债务重组计划时得到了一些喘息的机会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-court-adjourns-liquidation-hearing-china-developer-kaisa-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>1-4月全国规模以上工业利润增长4.3%，与一季度持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-profits-rise-43-jan-april-unchanged-q1-2024-05-27/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，今年前四个月中国工业企业利润同比增长4.3%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 01:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-profits-rise-43-jan-april-unchanged-q1-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>全球通胀数据公布前美元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-global-inflation-data-2024-05-27/</link><description>美元周一保持稳定，但预计将出现今年首次月度下跌，因为投资者关注美国、欧洲和日本通胀数据以指导全球利率前景。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 01:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-global-inflation-data-2024-05-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>